        Returns the scores for the given trios.
        Parameters:
        genotypesFilePath - The path to the genotype files.
        scoringData - The scoring data.
        childToParentMap - The child to parent map.
        model - The model to use.
        variableNames - The name of the variables.
        seScaling - The se scaling factor.
        bgenIndexFolder - The folder where to store the bgen index files.
        semaphore - The semaphore to use for the edition of the score map.
        logger - The logger to use to display feedback and errors.
        Returns:
        The scores for this model variables indexed by child id.
